songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Asian Doll]
Young bitch I got more cash then my own dad
Fuck a problem, I don't beef with that, I'm out to get a bag
Take a nigga, I just glo'd fast
Blasting on yo ass
Bought a Bentley truck can't wait to drive it in the hood so fast
Smoking trap I don't never pass
Soda, water, gas
Don't you speak, I don't got no name, I don't talk back
I ain't going fuck you tripping for, don't you call me boo
It's just me, I don't flirt with goofies, I'm too raw for you
Southside raised me
I ain't go to school cause Miss Harris was lazy
On my rapping shit
Getting so high, smoking juicy fruit
On the Main Street, William chicken, then it's dangerous
Hardly you will see me out so don't you come for me
We don't care about nobody gang
We riding with the heat, cautiously
I was born to be I was made to be
Tryna finesse over on anybody, ain't where I want to be
I had night I ain't eat a thing, too much up in the streets
Get away, I'm happy by myself
Can't never play a G
I ain't tricking on no bitch boy
You gone pay for me, you gone slave for me
For my meals hoe you a maid to me
You a coon
If you lie to me then we is not a we
I'm a doll, on that gang shit
Who they want to be
Told your bitch I don't sneak diss, quit trying to beef with me
I been pulling bitches whole card, like I'm Pokemon
Roll girl, you's a sweetswirl, lil kenda toughing shells
No stopping me, I am Asian, keep my doll she Cuban linked, Natalie
We gone take them trips, you bitches at the lake
I can teach you some swag school, called it aftermath
Get that money everyday shit, call it summer clap
Little girl you's a lame to me, you's a lame to me
You can't hang with the gang with me, can't rock no shows with me
You a sneaky bitch, don't you never point and smile at me
I do what I want so I jumped up on lil Kodak beat
I'm a bitch with some money, need some hundreds
You bitches gay y'all be stunting with niggas money
Want some glo, y'all so thirsty, we want the money, money
songs.title: No Flockin’
